  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are about 20m² and sleep up to three people. They have a bath with showerhead.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are about 20m² and sleep up to three people. They have a bath with showerhead.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are between 30-35m² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They have a small lounge area with elegant furnishings and a bath with showerhead.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are about 13m² and have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Classic Rooms for sole use</strong> are also available.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>General Information</strong></p>
<p>Check-in: 2pm</p>
<p>Check-out: 11am</p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €2.00 per person per day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
